quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,11,"Pellet, …ìen addu…ìe penaale …óen (…óum le ko tukkirgol bonki Yumma gom…óin…ìe …ìen Aa'isa yo Alla weltor mo) ko …ìe jamaa dammbitii…óo(askitiido) e moo…óon, -onon gom…óin…ìe …ìen- wata on sikku ko …ìe fefindii kon ko bone mo'on, ko woni, …óum ko mo∆¥∆¥ere sabu ko woni kon e mu'un immorde e mbarjaari e ndarndagol gom…óin…ìe …ìen, e ko jokki …óum kon e la…ì…ìinngol Yumma gom…óin…ìe …ìen. No woodani kala tawaa…óo e tukkirgol [NeenAa'isa] bonki njo…ìdi ko o faggitii kon immorde e junuubu sabu wowlugol makko ngol penaale …óen, e on fawtii…óo ko mawni kon e …óum sabu fu…ó…óagol makko …óum, no woodani mo Lepte maw…óe. Ko faandaa e …óum ko hooreejo naafiqii…ìe …ìen Abdullaahi bun Ubayyu bun Saluulu."
  24,12,"Ko haanunoo si wor…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen e rew…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen nanii …óee penaale maw…óe …ìe hooloo hisugol on mo …óum fenaa on e hoore-mu'un immorde e musi…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen, …ìe wi'a: "∆äum ko fenaande …ìanngunde nii"."
  24,13,"Ko haanunoo ko nde fefindii…ìe …ìen e dow Yumma gom…óin…ìe …ìen Aa'isa yo Alla weltor mo addaynoo seedee…ìe nayo e dow ngol fefindagol ma…ì…ìe mawngol, …ìe seedoo e dow sellugol ko …ìe dammbi kon e makko, si tawii …ìe addaali seedee…ìe nayo e dow …óum -te …ìe addataa …ìe poomaa- haray kam…ìe ko …ìe fenoo…ìe ka √ëaawoore Alla."
  24,14,"Sinndo wonaano ∆Åural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon -onon gom…óin…ìe …ìen- e Yurmeende Makko nden e moo…óon nde tawnoo O yaccinantaa on Lepte …óen, O la…ì…ìini …ìen tuubu…ìe immorde e muu…óon; he…ìayno on Lepte maw…óe sabu ko ukki…óon kon e mu'un immorde e fenaande e fefindagol e dow Yumma gom…óin…ìe …ìen."
  24,15,"Tuma yoga ma…ì…ìe fillantoo nde yoga, hi…óon eggira nde kunndu…óe moo…óon wonndude e bonugol mayre; alanah on e …óum ganndal, hi…óon sikka wonnde …óum ko newii…óum, hara le …óum ko mawnu…óum ka Alla; sabu ko woni kon e mu'un immorde e fenaande e tukkugol laa…ìu…óo."
  24,16,"Ko haanunoo tuma nanu…óon ndee fenaande, wi'on: "Sellantaa men nde men wowlata oo fiyaake kaanu…óo, Senayee wonanii Ma Joomi amen, ndee huunde nde …ìe werlii …óum e Yumma gom…óin…ìe …ìen ko fenaande mawnde"."
  24,17,"Alla no anndintinnde on O laa…ìana on fii wata on fillito yeru ndee fenaande werlo…óon bonki e laa…ìu…óo, si tawii on laatike gom…óin…ìe Alla."
  24,18,"Alla no …ìannginannde on Aayeeje moftu…óe …óen √ëaawooje Makko …óen e Waajuuji Makko …óin, Alla ko O Anndu…óo golle mon …óen, hay e huunde su…óanaaki e majje, aray O yo…ìa on e dow majje, ko O √ëee√±o ka Fewjoore Makko e ka Sari'a Makko."
  24,19,"Pellet, …ìen yi…óu…ìe yo pankare …óe lollu e hoore gom…óin…ìe …ìen -no jeyaa e majji tukkirgol jeeno ngon- no woodani …ìe Lepte muusu…óe ka aduna sabu √±imnugol hiddi tukkugol e dow ma…ì…ìe, no woodani …ìe kadi ka Laakara Lepte Yiite, Alla no Anndi penaale ma…ì…ìe …óen, e ko fiyakuuji jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen wontata, hiMo Anndi kadi nafaaji ma…ì…ìe …óin, onon on anndah …óum."
  24,20,"Sinndo wonaano ∆Åural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon -onon …ìee ukkii…ìe e penaale- e Yurmeende Makko nden e mo'on, sinndo wonaano pellet Alla ko O Newii…óo Hinnotoo…óo on, O yaccinanayno on Lepte …óen."